  tbody
    tr
      td Recovery Codes
      td Recovery codes can be used to access your account in the event you lose access to your device and cannot receive two-factor authentication codes. MMT cannot restore access to accounts with two-factor authentication enabled for security reasons, saving your recovery codes in a safe place can help keep you from being locked out of your account.
      td= link_to 'Recovery Codes', two_factor_recovery_codes_settings_path
    tr
      td Fallback SMS
      td Providing a fallback SMS number will allow MMT to send your two-factor authentication codes to an alternate device if you lose your primary device. For security reasons, MMT cannot restore access to accounts with two-factor authentication enabled. If you lose access to both your primary device and your recovery keys, a backup SMS number can get you back in to your account.
      td= link_to 'Add a fallback SMS number', two_factor_fallback_sms_settings_path
    tr
